translated: Francesco Canova da Milano says Francesco, born August 18, 1497 in Monza and died in 1543 in Milan is a lutenist and composer of the sixteenth century.
original: Francesco Canova, dit Francesco da Milano, né le 18 août 1497 à Monza et mort en 1543 à Milan est un luthiste et compositeur du XVIe siècle.
